      "html": "<p>原始印欧语根，意为“野兽”。</p><p>它构成了以下词语或部分： <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of baluchitherium \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/baluchitherium\">baluchitherium</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of feral \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/feral\">feral</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of ferine \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/ferine\">ferine</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of ferocious \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/ferocious\">ferocious</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of ferocity \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/ferocity\">ferocity</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of fierce \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/fierce\">fierce</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of ther- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/ther-\">ther-</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Theropoda \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Theropoda\">Theropoda</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of treacle \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/treacle\">treacle</a>。</p><p>它是假设的来源/其存在的证据由以下提供：拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">ferus</i> “野生的，未驯服的”； 希腊语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">thēr</i>，古教会斯拉夫语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">zveri</i>，立陶宛语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">žvėris</i> “野兽”。</p>"
